{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d738c01e-9b65-4061-a6ac-70e27d3fd55d","content":"Here's what you need for automatic crash dump collection with NativeAOT on .NET 11:\n\n**Environment variables** for your container:\n\n```yaml\nenv:\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n    value: \"1\"\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n    value: \"4\"                          # Full dump (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full)\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n    value: \"/tmp/dumps/core.%p.%t\"      # %p=PID, %t=timestamp\n  - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpPath\n    value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n```\n\n**Pod spec changes:**\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: your-app\n      # ... existing config ...\n      env:\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n          value: \"1\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n          value: \"4\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n          value: \"/tmp/dumps/core.%p.%t\"\n        - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpPath\n          value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: crash-dumps\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n      securityContext:\n        capabilities:\n          add: [\"SYS_PTRACE\"]           # Required for createdump to attach\n  volumes:\n    - name: crash-dumps\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi                  # Adjust based on expected dump size\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n| Setting | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `DOTNET_CreateDumpPath` | Tells the runtime where `createdump` lives |\n| `SYS_PTRACE` | Required — `createdump` uses `ptrace` to capture process memory |\n| `emptyDir` | Dumps persist until pod is deleted; swap for a PVC if you need durability |\n\nIf you want dumps to survive pod restarts, replace `emptyDir` with a `persistentVolumeClaim` or add a sidecar that ships dumps to object storage (e.g., S3/Azure Blob) before the pod terminates.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"65c69f3b-25ff-428e-b23b-bcf59ece364d","outputTokens":579,"requestId":"CB0F:E6727:1EE6FBC:222C9A5:6A0529F5"},"id":"f1798791-2766-4f46-a82a-fa340fa9e061","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:48:48.619Z","parentId":"478065cf-aa3b-4f4c-bdfb-5496b2e19c76"}
